data.description: Wonderful like new one level brick home on large level and fenced corner lot.  Open floor plan plus a 2 car garage, entrance on side.   Large formal dining room with 10' ceilings, great room has trey ceilings and open to the dining room. Breakfast room & kitchen and has access to the back covered patio. Nice sized kitchen, granite counter tops, stainless appliances, breakfast bar & breakfast room with view of the back yard. Large laundry room off kitchen. The master has double trey ceilings with a master bath that will not disappoint a large walk in closet, double sinks, soaking tub, separate tile shower. This is a split bedroom plan so two other bedrooms are separate from the master. The guest bathroom has tub showercombo. Granite countertops throughout, hardwoods in foyer, GR, hall and dining, tile in kitchen, breakfast room and baths.
